cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper deals with wireless communication systems and proposes a novel algorithm for rate selection in these systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves modeling and optimization, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper deals with practical wireless networks, which could place it in cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
